### Create a short URL
POST http://localhost:5000/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "originalUrl": "https://example.com/very/long/path",
  "maxClicks": 10,
  "windowSeconds": 60
}

### Resolve (follow redirect)
GET http://localhost:5000/r/{{code}}

### Get stats
GET http://localhost:5000/admin/{{code}}/stats
